latestIgtvVideos.title: Excessive dry hair, itchy scalp & hair fall ?? Homemade tareeka 😄😄
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
.
.
.
With simple ingredients. 👇👇👇👇
* Flaxseed (alsi)
* Water *Glycerin 👇👇👇👇
.
.
Apply twice in a week for best result ❣
.
.
.
*Flaxseeds* are rich in vitamin E, which is great for both skin and hair health. The nutrient promotes the health of the scalp by reducing free radical damage. It helps improve circulation in the head, thus promoting hair growth and slowing down hair breakage.
*Glycerin* helps in strengthening the hair, leading to less formation of split ends. Glycerin is heavy in humectants, which are made to pull moisture into the hair and retain it.
.
.
